{"tid":223233,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇養開蝸牛既巴打？","createTime":"2017-04-30T07:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T07:45:23.000Z","uid":82081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bec211c051134b46ba8f8bec2302fc293566c76","tid":223233,"uid":82081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:45:32.000Z","msg":"前日落完雨帶左佢返黎<br />\n上網睇過啲人養巴經驗話蘿蔔係好好既食材<br />\n但我比左佢又唔食<br />\n其實佢中意食咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZDBeTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZDBeTu.jpg&h=b29b89a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢地成日爬上盒頂倒立係咪正常？"},{"pid":"39e67883c709d12b154a99e9858ef8b4f139dd76","tid":223233,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:49:43.000Z","msg":"俾生菜啦"},{"pid":"deda85a66d96d7ba0fd0cbc67dff01547b4419d9","tid":223233,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"無啦啦捉走佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地老母會點諗？<br />\n你都有屋企人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa36003c1050bb650a6994953d81068f7ccb2e4","tid":223233,"uid":53568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"我上次睇左段片 見到隻蝸牛吃左隻蚯蚓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來佢個嘴可以張到勁大勁得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61389efb8250835ed12f71bbf1d5ca5717cf59e0","tid":223233,"uid":48266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:00:59.000Z","msg":"養過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要泥 水（唔好濕到水浸）<br />\n俾青瓜 生菜都得 <br />\n掉少少雞蛋殼碎俾佢（meet走殼入面層「衣」，蛋殼係補鈣用）<br />\n最好餵野食個陣拎佢上泥面，因為佢地好多時鑽入泥入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識食野<br />\n<br />\n利申bb養到變大牛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9w94S57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9