 />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9w94S57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9w94S57.jpg&h=3f07a349&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇話咩泥先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通泥（唔要入面有肥料成分）</blockquote><br />\n其實係咪因為我冇泥所以佢先成日爬上盒頂倒立??<br />\n你果D會唔會爬上盒頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59922460ba049be5676fec150444002898960935","tid":223233,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/162127_3f7fb538bf2fc9f8d0f650961a2beea5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F162127_3f7fb538bf2fc9f8d0f650961a2beea5.jpg&h=b75430ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蝸牛蝸牛"},{"pid":"ace566224bd358e5d5bb38e46f641135fb3a0e22","tid":223233,"uid":48266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>養過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要泥 水（唔好濕到水浸）<br />\n俾青瓜 生菜都得 <br />\n掉少少雞蛋殼碎俾佢（meet走殼入面層「衣」，蛋殼係補鈣用）<br />\n最好餵野食個陣拎佢上泥面，因為佢地好多時鑽入泥入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識食野<br />\n<br />\n利申bb養到變大牛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9w94S57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9w94S57.jpg&h=3f07a349&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇話咩泥先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普通泥（唔要入面有肥料成分）</blockquote><br />\n其實係咪因為我冇泥所以佢先成日爬上盒頂倒立??<br />\n你果D會唔會爬上盒頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常<br />\n我個啲都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ace71a5cd032711986bd2a19f24f4f349da0fd0","tid":223233,"uid":5775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:10:05.000Z","msg":"好得意!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想養好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但比老母話嘔心唔比養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9e843f2c4db33a0e196a1d689fea36ae252c250","tid":223233,"uid":38017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/162127_3f7fb538bf2fc9f8d0f650961a2beea5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F162127_3f7fb538bf2fc9f8d0f650961a2beea5.jpg&h=b75430ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蝸牛蝸牛</blockquote><br />\n好似同噴火駝同一個地方捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1595af600f111b424e20fd94ba518f9589f471","tid":223233,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/30/162127_3f7fb538bf2fc9f8d0f650961a2beea5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F30%2F162127_3f7fb538bf2fc9f8d0f650961a2beea5.jpg&h=b75430ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蝸牛蝸牛</blockquote><br />\n好似同噴火駝同一個地方捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪玩開385<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  熔岩蝸牛無得捉，捉熔岩蟲升上去進化"},{"pid":"f834597d7605fbab50b7ec7e363bdfba76b76643","tid":223233,"uid":62443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:34:50.000Z","msg":"好似就咁放入有植物嘅花盆放養就得<br />\n唔使困住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060349c75b8452a51c4c742d0375914aca2fa4d5","tid":223233,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:36:53.000Z","msg":"我又係落雨果陣執，養左7隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/033652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F033652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=854ad32e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1dcdb5c87674a388c5ee3939c4fdd983862a88a0","tid":223233,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:37:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似就咁放入有植物嘅花盆放養就得<br />\n唔使困住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一晚就走曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c732a64f9d3724cc410dee4c3fb3b847c36f107a","tid":223233,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:39:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前日落完雨帶左佢返黎<br />\n上網睇過啲人養巴經驗話蘿蔔係好好既食材<br />\n但我比左佢又唔食<br />\n其實佢中意食咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZDBeTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZDBeTu.jpg&h=b29b89a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同佢地成日爬上盒頂倒立係咪正常？</blockquote><br />\n佢地中意食生菜，偶爾可以喂下水果<br />\n千奇唔好餵有鹽分既食物<br />\n佢地倒吊係好正常既事，蝸牛都係傾向癡住墻壁或者天花板行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3326141502327c6dd474f2ec8612251a11d4e51d","tid":223233,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T19:44:10.000Z","msg":"仲有一個佢地唔落地既原因，就係有太多積水係地下，所以爬去相對乾爽既墻上面。<br />\n你可以鋪d吸水既底材係地下，保持潮濕又唔會有積水，佢地就會落返地下鳩爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a210eef527ff7ae72744b82149a4ed61276be8","tid":223233,"uid":82081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有一個佢地唔落地既原因，就係有太多積水係地下，所以爬去相對乾爽既墻上面。<br />\n你可以鋪d吸水既底材係地下，保持潮濕又唔會有積水，佢地就會落返地下鳩爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果隻都今日都仲唔肯食野.蘿蔔同菜葉都唔食.<br />\n餵埋佢口佢直行直過就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06c9345025e03ca3eff7fd6e432a9fd39751121","tid":223233,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我又係落雨果陣執，養左7隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/033652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F033652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=854ad32e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點解成日通街執野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f3c9084d622b2751e503b35257f4d5da92eb44","tid":223233,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:03:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我又係落雨果陣執，養左7隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/033652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F033652_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=854ad32e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點解成日通街執野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n精靈訓練員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edad96b20feca9f9b043de7e49e0ed24485b1283","tid":223233,"uid":28015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"蝸牛多唔多菌"},{"pid":"7d1967823653488e990073249b5aa19ab0198e93","tid":223233,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:41:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝸牛多唔多菌</blockquote><br />\n有大量寄生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ac497fe3e1937458ccc7c864baea8b8abc738f","tid":223233,"uid":82081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蝸牛多唔多菌</blockquote><br />\n有大量寄生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd02b8f2bcbd4357453e6e6c57df2ba15c69ba65","tid":223233,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蝸牛多唔多菌</blockquote><br />\n有大量寄生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔拎嚟生食都無乜問題"}]}